---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="About Blue Cap IT | Official Verkada Gold Partner">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> About</div>
      <div class="section-label">Who We Are</div>
      <h1>About <span class="grad">Blue Cap IT</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">A technology company specializing in Verkada physical security solutions. We combine local service with enterprise-grade technology to deliver exceptional results for our clients.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Our Mission</div>
          <h2>Making Enterprise Security<br/><span class="grad">Accessible.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT was founded with a simple mission: bring the most advanced physical security technology to businesses of all sizes — with the personal service of a local partner.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">As an official Verkada Gold Partner, we provide access to a world-class security platform that was previously only accessible to large enterprises. We handle everything from first consultation to installation to long-term support.</p>
          <div class="verkada-gold-section">
            <img src="/verkada-gold-partner-badge.png" alt="Verkada Gold Partner" style="height:52px;width:auto;flex-shrink:0;"/>
            <p><strong>Verkada Gold Partner Program Member.</strong> This status reflects our commitment to Verkada's platform, our technical expertise, and the trust our clients place in us.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Contact Our Team</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">★</div>
            <div><h4>Verkada Gold Partner Status</h4><p>We hold official Verkada Gold Partner status — meaning access to the full product catalog, partner pricing, Verkada technical resources, and manufacturer support for our clients.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">📍</div>
            <div><h4>Local, Responsive Service</h4><p>We're local. Our team provides the hands-on support and quick response times that remote providers simply can't match.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🤝</div>
            <div><h4>Relationship-Driven Support</h4><p>When you call (410) 858-4031 or email <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" style="color:var(--blue);">info@bluecapit.com</a>, you reach a real person who knows your system. We build long-term partnerships, not just one-time transactions.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔒</div>
            <div><h4>Security-First Mindset</h4><p>We understand that physical security is serious. We approach every project with the rigor, care, and professionalism that protecting your people and assets demands.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRODUCT FAMILY SHOT -->
  <section style="padding:1rem 4% 5rem;background:var(--off-white);">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="section-label">What We Deliver</div>
      <h2>The Full Verkada <span class="grad">Platform</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto 2rem;">From cameras and access control to sensors, alarms, intercom, and wireless — Blue Cap IT delivers the complete Verkada ecosystem.</p>
      <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Blue Cap IT" class="img-hero-band"/>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PARTNER SECTION -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">Our Partnership</div>
      <h2>Official Verkada <span class="grad">Gold Partner</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0.8rem auto 1.5rem;">Verkada is the industry leader in cloud-managed physical security. Blue Cap IT is proud to be an official Verkada Gold Partner — giving our clients access to the best security technology available.</p>
      <img src="/verkada-gold-partner-badge.png" alt="Verkada Gold Partner" style="height:80px;width:auto;margin:0 auto 2rem;display:block;"/>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:1.2rem;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.8rem 1rem;"><div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;">🥇</div><div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.3rem;">Gold Partner</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Authorized Verkada Reseller</div></div>
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.8rem 1rem;"><div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;">📦</div><div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.3rem;">Full Catalog</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);">All Verkada Products &amp; Licenses</div></div>
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.8rem 1rem;"><div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;">🛡️</div><div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.3rem;">Warranty Backed</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);">10-Year Hardware Warranty</div></div>
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.8rem 1rem;"><div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;">🤝</div><div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.3rem;">Dual Support</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Blue Cap IT + Verkada Engineering</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Work With Us</div>
    <h2>Let's Secure Your<br/><span class="grad">Business Together</span></h2>
    <p>Contact Blue Cap IT today to start a conversation about your security needs. Free consultations, transparent pricing, no pressure.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
